STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
O.C. HIGHTOWER, a/k/a Hightower O.C., Webb William, Defendant-Petitioner. C-803 September Term 2017
080481 Supreme Court of New Jersey. April 24, 2018

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION.

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005298-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
